---
---
<section class="relative isolate overflow-hidden py-24">
  <div class="absolute inset-0 -z-10 bg-gradient-to-br from-slate-950 via-slate-900 to-slate-950"></div>
  <div class="absolute left-1/2 top-0 -z-10 h-[28rem] w-[36rem] -translate-x-1/2 rounded-full bg-sky-500/20 blur-3xl"></div>
  <div class="absolute -right-24 bottom-[-6rem] -z-10 h-80 w-80 rounded-full bg-sky-400/10 blur-3xl"></div>

  <div class="mx-auto grid max-w-6xl items-center gap-16 px-6 lg:grid-cols-[minmax(0,1.1fr)_minmax(0,0.9fr)]">
    <div>
      <span class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 rounded-full border border-sky-500/40 bg-slate-900/70 px-4 py-1 text-xs font-semibold uppercase tracking-[0.25em] text-sky-300">
        tecnologia confiável
      </span>
      <h1 class="mt-6 text-4xl font-semibold leading-tight text-slate-50 md:text-6xl">
        Transformamos tecnologia em resultados que inspiram confiança
      </h1>
      <p class="mt-5 max-w-2xl text-lg text-slate-300">
        Projetos digitais sob medida, arquitetura escalável e uma equipe que fala a língua do seu negócio. Da estratégia à
        entrega, cada etapa é pensada para gerar impacto real.
      </p>
      <div class="mt-8 flex flex-col gap-3 sm:flex-row">
        <a
          href="/contact"
          class="inline-flex items-center justify-center rounded-full bg-sky-500 px-7 py-3 text-base font-semibold text-slate-950 shadow-lg shadow-sky-950/40 transition hover:bg-sky-400"
        >
          Solicitar orçamento
        </a>
        <a
          href="/services"
          class="inline-flex items-center justify-center rounded-full border border-slate-700/70 bg-slate-900/60 px-7 py-3 text-base font-semibold text-slate-200 transition hover:border-sky-400/60 hover:text-sky-200"
        >
          Ver serviços
        </a>
      </div>
      <div class="mt-12 grid gap-6 text-sm text-slate-300 sm:grid-cols-3">
        <div class="rounded-2xl border border-slate-800/70 bg-slate-900/60 p-5">
          <p class="text-2xl font-semibold text-slate-50">+10 anos</p>
          <p class="mt-1 text-slate-400">Construindo soluções digitais de alta performance.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="rounded-2xl border border-slate-800/70 bg-slate-900/60 p-5">
          <p class="text-2xl font-semibold text-slate-50">Equipe senior</p>
          <p class="mt-1 text-slate-400">Especialistas em produto, engenharia e experiência.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="rounded-2xl border border-slate-800/70 bg-slate-900/60 p-5">
          <p class="text-2xl font-semibold text-slate-50">Entrega segura</p>
          <p class="mt-1 text-slate-400">Processos auditáveis, métricas claras e foco em confiabilidade.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="relative rounded-3xl border border-slate-800/70 bg-slate-900/60 p-10 shadow-2xl shadow-slate-950/40">
      <div class="mb-8 flex items-center justify-between text-sm text-slate-400">
        <span class="font-medium text-slate-200">Painel de projetos</span>
        <span class="rounded-full border border-slate-700/70 px-3 py-1 text-xs uppercase tracking-[0.2em]">Status</span>
      </div>
      <div class="space-y-6">
        <div>
          <div class="flex items-center justify-between">
            <p class="font-semibold text-slate-100">Onboarding digital</p>
            <span class="text-xs font-semibold text-sky-300">em desenvolvimento</span>
          </div>
          <div class="mt-2 h-2 rounded-full bg-slate-800">
            <div class="h-full w-3/4 rounded-full bg-sky-500"></div>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div>
          <div class="flex items-center justify-between">
            <p class="font-semibold text-slate-100">Plataforma B2B</p>
            <span class="text-xs font-semibold text-green-400">entregue</span>
          </div>
          <div class="mt-2 h-2 rounded-full bg-slate-800">
            <div class="h-full w-full rounded-full bg-green-400"></div>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div>
          <div class="flex items-center justify-between">
            <p class="font-semibold text-slate-100">Aplicativo logístico</p>
            <span class="text-xs font-semibold text-amber-300">kickoff</span>
          </div>
          <div class="mt-2 h-2 rounded-full bg-slate-800">
            <div class="h-full w-1/4 rounded-full bg-amber-300"></div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="mt-10 rounded-2xl border border-slate-800 bg-slate-950/80 p-6">
        <p class="text-sm uppercase tracking-[0.25em] text-slate-500">Satisfação média</p>
        <p class="mt-3 text-4xl font-semibold text-slate-50">9.6</p>
        <p class="mt-2 text-sm text-slate-400">Baseado no feedback de clientes corporativos nos últimos 12 meses.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
